    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_1009695121990616796.png",
                "id": "talent83413",
                "key": "拂金剑斗术 ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "拂金剑斗术 "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">净焰剑狱领域</span>；如果已存在净焰剑狱领域，就先造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/862a5d3d2d4443f7f5068402b95c43c7_6001010519085421535.png",
                "id": "talent19799",
                "key": "熔铁流狱",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熔铁流狱"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，然后<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">准备技能</span>：<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">焚落踢</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/0a9de135471ab849dba578dcf95ebb6d_2192277525760721505.png",
                "id": "talent91148",
                "key": "炎啸狮子咬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "炎啸狮子咬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p>结束阶段：造成1点<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">当此召唤物在场且迪希雅在我方后台，我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消1点伤害；然后，如果迪希雅生命至少为7，则对其造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1635374446173542987.png",
                "id": "talent2013",
                "key": "净焰剑狱领域",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/d85d7163eca60bd55a1624838144701a_1224163297260995778.png",
                "title": "净焰剑狱领域"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_7012901917327080860.png",
                "id": "talent94690",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">准备技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>。轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动；如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要准备的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」「角色引发元素反应后」等效果。）只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">焚落踢</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1765077866789030751.png",
                "id": "talent71219",
                "key": "规则术语",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "规则术语"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
